---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/CTASection';
import Reviews from '../../components/Reviews';
import ServiceForm from '../../components/ServiceForm';
import LicenseBadges from '../../components/LicenseBadges.astro';
import BrandsSection from '../../components/BrandsSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Air Conditioning Repair Santa Ana | HiLo Heating and Air" description="Expert AC repair and furnace repair in Santa Ana, CA. Fast, reliable HVAC service from licensed technicians at HiLo Heating and Air.">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-blue-800 py-20 sm:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Air Conditioning Repair Santa Ana & Furnace Repair Santa Ana</h1>
        <p class="text-white/80 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">Santa Ana swings between brutal summer heat and surprisingly cold winter nights. When your HVAC system gives out, HiLo Heating and Air picks up fast.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-10 pb-4 sm:py-16 sm:pb-6 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <LicenseBadges />
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-10 items-start">
          <div>
            <span class="inline-block bg-brand-blue/10 text-brand-blue text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4">Schedule Service</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-4">Get a Free Estimate</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Fill out the form and our team will get back to you within 15 minutes. Same-day service available.</p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Same-Day Service Available</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Free Diagnostics with Repair</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0115.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 013 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 00-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 003 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Upfront Pricing, No Hidden Fees</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ServiceForm client:load />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-blue mt-0 mb-4">HVAC Services in Santa Ana</h2>

        <p>Santa Ana swings between brutal summer heat and surprisingly cold winter nights, so your HVAC system pretty much never gets a break. When it finally gives out, you need someone who picks up fast — which is exactly why locals call HiLo Heating and Air for <strong>air conditioning repair Santa Ana</strong> and <strong>furnace repair Santa Ana</strong> problems alike.</p>

        <h2>When Your AC Gives Out</h2>
        <p>A dead air conditioner in the middle of July isn't just uncomfortable — for kids, older folks, or anyone with health issues, it can actually be dangerous. Our <strong>air conditioning repair Santa Ana</strong> techs know this city's homes well, whether it's an older unit in Floral Park or a newer system out near South Coast Metro. We get there quickly, usually the same day, and we actually figure out what's wrong instead of throwing parts at it.</p>
        <p>Most of the time it's one of a few things: low refrigerant, a dying capacitor, an electrical short, or a compressor that's finally calling it quits. Our trucks are stocked for it, so most <strong>air conditioning repair Santa Ana</strong> calls get wrapped up in one visit — you're not sweating it out for days waiting on a follow-up.</p>

        <h2>Furnace Not Kicking On?</h2>
        <p>Don't ignore it once the temperature drops. Our <strong>furnace repair Santa Ana</strong> crew handles pilot light and ignition trouble, blower motor failures, thermostat issues, and airflow problems from clogged filters or blocked ducts. We work on gas and electric furnaces, every major brand, so whatever's sitting in your closet, we'll know it.</p>
        <p>A furnace that's been neglected doesn't just mean a chilly house — it can mean a higher gas bill, or worse, a carbon monoxide risk in older gas units. That's why every <strong>furnace repair Santa Ana</strong> job includes a full safety check, not just the fix itself.</p>

        <h2>Why Santa Ana Picks HiLo</h2>
        <p>Bigger companies tend to rotate random crews through your neighborhood — you never know who's showing up. HiLo Heating and Air does it differently. Same trusted techs, honest pricing upfront, no pressure to replace something that just needs fixing. We're licensed, insured, and trained on Carrier, Trane, Lennox, Goodman, Rheem, and pretty much everything in between.</p>
        <p>Summer or winter, <strong>air conditioning repair Santa Ana</strong> or <strong>furnace repair Santa Ana</strong>, the approach stays the same: get there fast, diagnose it honestly, charge a fair price.</p>

        <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
        <p>Don't let a small issue turn into a costly breakdown. Reach out to HiLo Heating and Air today.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    

    <Reviews client:visible />
    <BrandsSection />

    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-slate-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">How fast can you get to my house?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Usually same-day, and often within a couple hours if it's urgent.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">How do I know my furnace needs repair?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Cold air instead of warm, odd banging or clicking sounds, the system cycling too often, or a gas bill that's suddenly higher than usual.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Do you do emergency calls after hours?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Yep — evenings and weekends included, for both AC and furnace issues.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">What's a repair going to cost?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Depends on the problem, but you'll know the price before we start anything. No surprises later.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Do you handle every brand?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Carrier, Trane, Lennox, Goodman, Rheem — basically all the major ones.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Should I just replace my system instead of fixing it?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Only if it actually makes sense. We'll tell you straight based on age and condition, not push a sale.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Any maintenance plans?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Yes, seasonal plans that catch the small stuff before it turns into a bigger repair.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Are your techs licensed?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Every single one — licensed, insured, background-checked.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-brand-blue/5 py-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-brand-blue font-semibold">HiLo Heating and Air · 8131 Electric Ave, Stanton, CA 90680, United States</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-1"><a href="tel:+17148535534" class="hover:text-brand-red transition">(714) 853-5534</a> · <a href="mailto:info@hiloheatingandair.com" class="hover:text-brand-red transition">info@hiloheatingandair.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <CTASection client:visible />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
